.el .ds Aq '
.TH cando-log-analyzer 1  "cando-log-analyzer 0.1.0" 
.SH NAME
cando\-log\-analyzer \- CAN Log Analyzer \- Parse candump logs with comprehensive DBC decoding (J1939)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcando\-log\-analyzer\fR [\fB\-d\fR|\fB\-\-decoded\-only\fR] [\fB\-f\fR|\fB\-\-device\-filter\fR] [\fB\-m\fR|\fB\-\-message\-filter\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-s\fR|\fB\-\-statistics\fR] [\fB\-\-export\-json\fR] [\fB\-\-export\-csv\fR] [\fB\-o\fR|\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-\-csv\fR] [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-\-text\fR] [\fB\-t\fR|\fB\-\-timing\-analysis\fR] [\fB\-l\fR|\fB\-\-limit\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fILOG_FILE\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
CAN Log Analyzer \- Parse candump logs with comprehensive DBC decoding (J1939)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-d\fR, \fB\-\-decoded\-only\fR
Show only decoded messages (hide unknown)
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-device\-filter\fR \fI<DEVICE_FILTER>\fR
Filter by specific device IDs (comma\-separated hex values)
.TP
\fB\-m\fR, \fB\-\-message\-filter\fR \fI<MESSAGE_FILTER>\fR
Filter by message name patterns (comma\-separated)
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Show detailed signal analysis
.TP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-statistics\fR
Show statistics summary
.TP
\fB\-\-export\-json\fR \fI<EXPORT_JSON>\fR
Export decoded data to JSON file
.TP
\fB\-\-export\-csv\fR \fI<EXPORT_CSV>\fR
Export decoded data to CSV file
.TP
\fB\-o\fR, \fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR [default: text]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
text: Human\-readable text format (default)
.IP \(bu 2
csv: Comma\-separated values format
.IP \(bu 2
json: JSON format
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-csv\fR
Output in CSV format (same as \-\-output=csv)
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Output in JSON format (same as \-\-output=json)
.TP
\fB\-\-text\fR
Output in text format (same as \-\-output=text)
.TP
\fB\-t\fR, \fB\-\-timing\-analysis\fR
Show message timing analysis
.TP
\fB\-l\fR, \fB\-\-limit\fR \fI<LIMIT>\fR
Limit number of messages to process (for large files)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
<\fILOG_FILE\fR>
Path to candump log file
.SH VERSION
v0.1.0
